ííŸ@0685c745646a36e1fc56e264cfb85a061b61a3e4f385dabe954e139c4627ae8d⁄mTitle: This week in Nushell #90
Path: Nushell
Content:
jonathandturner 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/issues/3428] made the default int an i64
, fixed an issue with 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/issues/3422] path variable casing on Windows
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/issues/3415] improved missing var in var-path error
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/issues/3413] do less work in 
``sys``
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/issues/3412] fixed string interp/shorthand overlap
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/issues/3411] bumped to 0.31.1
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/issues/3405] released 0.31.0
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/issues/3401] simplified string interpolation
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/issues/3389] simplify base expressions
elferherrera added a 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/issues/3424] Dataframe feature for plugins
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/issues/3417] commands to engine p
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/issues/3410] ported date commands to engine p
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/issues/3408] config commands to engine p
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/issues/3404] more commands to engine p
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/issues/3373] Complete Dataframe MVP
Sympatron updated 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/issues/3420] case-insensitive completion matching by default on Windows
fdncred 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/issues/3409] made seq more nu-like by returning numbers when possible
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/issues/3403] added into string
lily-mara 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/issues/3407] removed unnecessary work from ps
alexshadley 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/issues/3406] migrated last to engine-p
kubouch 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/issues/3399] converted the rest of "random" subcommands to engine-p
stormasm update 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/issues/3394] engine-p: build-string remove ActionStream
